There are no prior works for ConvQA over heterogeneous sources. Thus, to compare the proposed \convinse pipeline with alternative choices, we adapt state-of-the-art question understanding (in this case, rewriting and resolution) methods from the IR and NLP literature.
These serve as competitors for our SR generation phase. We then provide these baselines with exactly the same ERS and HA phases that \convinse has, to complete end-to-end QA pipelines.